Beloved gospel artist, Pastor Neyi Zimu, has died. JOHANNESBURG - The funeral service of Gospel sensation Pastor Neyi Zimu is underway at the House of Treasures Ministries church in Rispark, Johannesburg. Zimu died at Busamed Hospital in Modderfontein last Wednesday while undergoing treatment for skin cancer. He was 49. READ: Neyi Zimu lovingly remembered Mourners have gathered at the church to bid farewell to the late gospel star and pastor. He will later be laid to rest at Kromvlei Cemetery in Alberton.